---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="ICN Use Cases" description="Real-world applications of the InterCooperative Network">
  
  <section class="pt-32 pb-16">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold mb-6 text-white">Real-World ICN Applications</h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-light-slate max-w-4xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
          ICN enables new forms of democratic coordination, cooperative economics, and 
          community-controlled technology. Explore concrete examples of how organizations 
          are using ICN to build post-capitalist infrastructure.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Use Case Examples -->
      <div class="space-y-16">
        
        <!-- Worker Cooperative Example -->
        <div class="use-case-card">
          <div class="use-case-header">
            <div class="use-case-tag bg-accent-primary/20 text-accent-primary">Worker Cooperative</div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-2">TechCoop Collective</h3>
            <p class="text-light-slate">Distributed Software Development Cooperative</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
            <div>
              <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4">The Challenge</h4>
              <p class="text-light-slate mb-6">
                45 software developers across 12 countries needed democratic governance 
                for project allocation, profit sharing, and member admission while 
                maintaining technical coordination.
              </p>
              
              <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4">ICN Solution</h4>
              <ul class="text-light-slate space-y-2">
                <li>• CoVM instance running democratic voting on all major decisions</li>
                <li>• Automated profit-sharing based on contribution tracking</li>
                <li>• Mesh computing for distributed CI/CD environments</li>
                <li>• Mana allocation for resource usage and priority setting</li>
                <li>• Federation connections with other tech cooperatives</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Implementation Focus</h4>
              <ul class="text-light-slate space-y-2">
                <li>• Transparent democratic decision-making processes</li>
                <li>• Automated profit distribution based on cooperative principles</li>
                <li>• Reduced administrative overhead through CoVM automation</li>
                <li>• Enhanced member engagement through AgoraNet deliberation</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Community Governance Example -->
        <div class="use-case-card">
          <div class="use-case-header">
            <div class="use-case-tag bg-accent-blue/20 text-accent-blue">Community Governance</div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Riverside Neighborhood Council</h3>
            <p class="text-light-slate">Democratic Municipal Governance Platform</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
            <div>
              <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4">The Challenge</h4>
              <p class="text-light-slate mb-6">
                2,400 residents needed better democratic participation in local 
                decisions about budget allocation, development projects, and 
                community programs with authentic resident verification.
              </p>
              
              <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4">ICN Solution</h4>
              <ul class="text-light-slate space-y-2">
                <li>• Constitutional CoVM with resident verification system</li>
                <li>• Participatory budgeting with transparent voting</li>
                <li>• Verified resident identities preventing manipulation</li>
                <li>• Guardian Circles for restorative justice</li>
                <li>• Integration with municipal systems</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Key Benefits</h4>
              <ul class="text-light-slate space-y-2">
                <li>• Increased civic participation through accessible digital tools</li>
                <li>• Transparent budget allocation and democratic oversight</li>
                <li>• Community-driven policy development and implementation</li>
                <li>• Enhanced trust through verifiable governance processes</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Mutual Aid Network Example -->
        <div class="use-case-card">
          <div class="use-case-header">
            <div class="use-case-tag bg-accent-purple/20 text-accent-purple">Mutual Aid Network</div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-2">HealthNet Mutual Aid Federation</h3>
            <p class="text-light-slate">Cooperative Healthcare Resource Sharing</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
            <div>
              <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4">The Challenge</h4>
              <p class="text-light-slate mb-6">
                23 health cooperatives across three states needed coordination 
                for resource sharing, emergency response, and collective purchasing 
                while maintaining local autonomy.
              </p>
              
              <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4">ICN Solution</h4>
              <ul class="text-light-slate space-y-2">
                <li>• Federation governance for shared policies</li>
                <li>• Resource sharing with mana-based fair allocation</li>
                <li>• Emergency response coordination</li>
                <li>• Collective purchasing through federated voting</li>
                <li>• Privacy-preserving health data sharing</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Core Capabilities</h4>
              <ul class="text-light-slate space-y-2">
                <li>• Federated resource sharing across cooperative networks</li>
                <li>• Emergency response coordination with democratic oversight</li>
                <li>• Collective purchasing power through federated decision-making</li>
                <li>• Privacy-preserving data sharing between health cooperatives</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>

      <!-- Implementation Steps -->
      <div class="mt-20">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12 text-white">Ready to Implement ICN?</h2>
        
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
          <div class="step-card">
            <div class="step-number">01</div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Assessment & Planning</h3>
            <p class="text-light-slate mb-6">
              Evaluate your organization's needs, governance structure, and technical requirements.
            </p>
            <a href="/docs/assessment" class="step-button">Assessment Guide</a>
          </div>

          <div class="step-card">
            <div class="step-number">02</div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Pilot Deployment</h3>
            <p class="text-light-slate mb-6">
              Start with a limited scope pilot to test governance processes and train users.
            </p>
            <a href="/docs/deployment/pilot" class="step-button">Pilot Guide</a>
          </div>

          <div class="step-card">
            <div class="step-number">03</div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Full Implementation</h3>
            <p class="text-light-slate mb-6">
              Scale to full organizational use with production infrastructure and governance.
            </p>
            <a href="/docs/deployment/production" class="step-button">Production Guide</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Call to Action -->
      <div class="mt-20 text-center bg-gradient-to-br from-accent-primary/10 to-accent-blue/10 p-12 rounded-lg border border-accent-primary/30">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6 text-white">Start Your ICN Journey</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-light-slate mb-8 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          ICN is ready for real-world deployment. Join the growing network of cooperatives, 
          communities, and federations building post-capitalist infrastructure.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
          <a href="/get-started" class="btn-primary">Get Started</a>
          <a href="/community" class="btn-secondary">Join Community</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .use-case-card {
    background: rgba(17, 34, 64, 0.3);
    border: 1px solid rgba(50, 255, 210, 0.2);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 2rem;
  }

  .use-case-header {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .use-case-tag {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
    border-radius: 20px;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }



  .step-card {
    background: rgba(17, 34, 64, 0.5);
    border: 1px solid rgba(50, 255, 210, 0.2);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 2rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .step-number {
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-accent-glow);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .step-button {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
    background: rgba(50, 255, 210, 0.1);
    border: 1px solid rgba(50, 255, 210, 0.3);
    color: var(--color-accent-glow);
    text-decoration: none;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-weight: 500;
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
  }

  .step-button:hover {
    background: rgba(50, 255, 210, 0.2);
    border-color: rgba(50, 255, 210, 0.5);
  }

  .btn-primary {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 0.75rem 2rem;
    background: var(--color-accent-glow);
    color: var(--color-midnight-navy);
    font-weight: 600;
    border-radius: 8px;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
  }

  .btn-primary:hover {
    background: rgba(50, 255, 210, 0.9);
    transform: scale(1.05);
  }

  .btn-secondary {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 0.75rem 2rem;
    background: transparent;
    color: var(--color-accent-glow);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-accent-glow);
    font-weight: 600;
    border-radius: 8px;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
  }

  .btn-secondary:hover {
    background: var(--color-accent-glow);
    color: var(--color-midnight-navy);
  }
</style> 